entry.title: Foundry Mews
entry.propertyDescription:
Nestled discreetly along the charming stretch of Barnes High Street lies Foundry Mews a courtyard development. The commercial complex offers a harmonious blend of contemporary workspace set amidst serene surroundings. Developed and managed by Marston Properties, this modern workspace seamlessly provides a tranquil environment ideal for small businesses to thrive.

We have availability of two commercial units in Autumn 2024, ranging from 775 to 850 sq ft. For further information please contact Marston Properties.
